Ahead of the much anticipated “The Shine Ya Eye Lockdown” reunion, one of the former housemates, Beatrice Agba Nwaji has promised some ‘gbas gbos.’ The reality TV star, revealing what she would be bringing to the reunion, unapologetically said she would be giving it hard to two of her colleagues who continued to talk about her even after the show. Beatrice didn’t state the names of these housemates but wrote: ““I came ready for the two people that couldn’t get my name off their mouth even after BBN show. No regrets!”   Why I prefer braids to wearing wigs, by Adesua Etomi     RMD’s daughter to men: allow me break your heart…     Grateful I was not part of RHWOL show-Ka3na   On May 19, organisers of Big Brother reality show, announced June 2 for BBNaija Season 6 ‘Shine Ya Eye’ reunion via their twitter handle “The Shine Ya Eye Lockdown reunion is back. Starts June 2, showing Mondays to Friday 10pm on AM Urban, 10:30 on AM Family,” it said. The reunion show will be hosted by Ebuka Obi Uchendu, who will revisit some highlights and memorable moments from the 2021 season 6 edition won by WhiteMoney.